<%# Brand card for use inside _brands_cards.html.erb
    Each card has a logo area, descriptive text, and a footnote.

    Locals:
      text:     (String) description text
      footnote: (String) footnote text (e.g. "Investor in X, Y, Z.")

    Usage: Provide the logo content in the yielded block.

    Example:
      render "shared/marketing/brands_cards_item", text: "Focused capital for founders.", footnote: "Investor in Acme, Inc." do
        <img src="/placeholder.webp" alt="Brand logo" class="h-8">
      end
%>

<div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-6 rounded-xl bg-mist-950/2.5 p-6 dark:bg-white/5">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-2">
    <div class="flex h-8 shrink-0"><%= yield %></div>
    <p class="text-sm/7 text-mist-700 dark:text-mist-400"><%= text %></p>
  </div>
  <p class="text-xs/6 text-mist-700 dark:text-mist-400"><%= footnote %></p>
</div>
